============
filebot -script fn:amc "K:\Tv Shows" --output "H:\Renamed" --log-file amc.log --action duplicate --conflict override -non-strict --def artwork=n subtitles=en "seriesFormat={Plex}" "movieFormat={Plex}" clean=y

============

Fetch Artwork and Nfo for Movies

//Rips Poseter.jpg, fanart.jpg, banner.jpg, folder.jpg and Logo.jpg. generates .nfo

filebot -script fn:artwork.tmdb D:\Movies -non-strict

============

Fetch Artwork and Nfo for TV Shows

//Rips Poseter.jpg, fanart.jpg, banner.jpg, folder.jpg and Logo.jpg. generates .nfo

filebot -script fn:artwork.tvdb K:\TvShows -non-strict

============

Fetch Artwork and Nfo for Anime

//Rips Poseter.jpg, fanart.jpg, banner.jpg, folder.jpg and Logo.jpg. generates .nfo

filebot -script fn:artwork.tvdb "G:\Archive01\Anime" -non-strict

============

How to include Poster in show For local pull.
============
So what can you add to TV show sections?

    Show posters: show.jpg
    Show banners: banner.jpg
    Show background art: art.jpg or background.jpg
    Show theme music: theme.mp3
    Season posters: seasonX.jpg
    Season banners: seasonX-banner.jpg
    Episode thumbs: match the filename of the episode file
===========
